name: Tank Maze
tagline: Tank game to go through a maze full of enemies and bombs trying to reach the enemy's base and destroy it.
body:
![Logo](https://github.com/Magdz/TankMaze/blob/master/TankMaze/Assets/TankMazeLogo.png)
[Download the Game Here.](https://github.com/Magdz/TankMaze/releases/download/v1.0/TankMaze.exe)
# TankMaze
Move through the maze and reach the enemy base and destroy it.
Watch out from the bombs and the enemies.
break the walls, and collect the gifts as you move through.
